title: Star_Fucking_Hipsters-Until_Were_Dead-2008-FNT
description:
Straight out of the squats of NYC, Star Fucking Hipsters are a veritable who&#039;s who of the punk/ska/crust scene.  Originally the brainchild of Leftover Crack vocalist Scott Sturgeon and drummer Brandon Chevalier-Kolling in 2004, Star Fucking Hipsters was temporarily derailed by Brandon&#039;s tragic and untimely death.
  In 2007, Sturg and original LOC drummer Ara Babajian joined forces with friends Frank Piegara (The Degenerics, Ensign, Fanshen), Nico de Gaillo (Another Dying Democracy, The Randalls, Casa de Chihuahua) and Yula Beeri (Nanuchka, ex-World/Inferno Friendship Society) to bring you Until We&#039;re Dead
